{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"short_name","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/short_name","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","browserCompat":["html.manifest.short_name"],"baseline":{"baseline":false,"support":{"chrome":"53","chrome_android":"53","edge":"79","firefox_android":"79","safari":"17","safari_ios":"15.4"}},"sidebarHTML":"\n<ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/background_color\">background_color</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/categories\">categories</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/description\">description</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/display\">display</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/display_override\">display_override</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/file_handlers\">file_handlers</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/icons\">icons</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/id\">id</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/launch_handler\">launch_handler</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/name\">name</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/orientation\">orientation</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/prefer_related_applications\">prefer_related_applications</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/protocol_handlers\">protocol_handlers</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/related_applications\">related_applications</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/scope\">scope</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/screenshots\">screenshots</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/serviceworker\">serviceworker</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/share_target\">share_target</a></li><li><em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/short_name\" aria-current=\"page\">short_name</a></em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/shortcuts\">shortcuts</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/start_url\">start_url</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/theme_color\">theme_color</a></li></ol>\n","sidebarMacro":"QuickLinksWithSubpages","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <code>short_name</code> manifest member is used to specify a short name for your web application, which may be used when the full <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/name\"><code>name</code></a> is too long for the available space.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><div class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">json</span></div><pre class=\"brush: json notranslate\"><code>/* Short names of web apps */\n\"short_name\": \"TaskPlanner\"\n\"short_name\": \"RecipePantry\"\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"values","title":"Values","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"short_name\"><a href=\"#short_name\"><code>short_name</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A string that specifies a short version of your web app's <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/name\"><code>name</code></a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"Description","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Browsers may use <code>short_name</code> in place of <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/name\"><code>name</code></a> when there is insufficient space to display the full name, such as on a device's home screen, in the application switcher, or in other space-constrained contexts.</p>\n<p>Keep the following points in mind when selecting a short name for your web app:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>It should be a concise version of your app's <code>name</code>.</li>\n  <li>While aiming for brevity, it should still be recognizable and meaningful.</li>\n  <li>Consider how it will appear in space-constrained contexts.</li>\n  <li>Follow the same guidelines for cultural sensitivity and trademark as for <code>name</code>.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"adding_a_short_name_for_your_web_app","title":"Adding a short name for your web app","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Consider a web app that helps users plan and log their hiking adventures. The <code>name</code> has been defined as <code>Trail Navigator</code>. A <code>short_name</code> can be added to the manifest as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><div class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">json</span></div><pre class=\"brush: json notranslate\"><code>\"name\": \"Trail Navigator\",\n\"short_name\": \"TrailNav\"\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>The app's shorter name <code>TrailNav</code> is concise and is suitable for limited space contexts. It maintains a connection to the app's full name and is easy to remember.</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/manifest/#short_name-member","title":"Web Application Manifest"}],"query":"html.manifest.short_name"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"html.manifest.short_name"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/name\"><code>name</code></a> manifest member</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Progressive_web_apps/Guides/Making_PWAs_installable#the_web_app_manifest\">The web app manifest</a> for making your web app installable</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Description","id":"description"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The short_name manifest member is used to specify a short name for your web application, which may be used when the full name is too long for the available space.","popularity":0.0016,"modified":"2020-10-15T22:19:34.266Z","other_translations":[],"pageType":"web-manifest-member","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/manifest/short_name","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/manifest/short_name/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/null","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"short_name","parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"References"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest","title":"Web app manifests"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/short_name","title":"short_name"}],"pageTitle":"short_name - Web app manifests | MDN","noIndexing":false},"url":"/en-US/docs/Web/Manifest/short_name"}